Verein zur Förderung von GNUnet e.V.
====================================

This repository contains the Satzung, list of members and other documents
of the Verein zur Förderung von GNUnet e.V.


To build the documents which can be build,
on a Debian-based system:

apt-get install texinfo \
                install texlive \
                texlive-lang-german \
                texlive-latex-extra \
                texlive-latex-extra \
                texlive-publishers \
                texlive-latex-humanities \
                texlive-humanities

cd gnunet-ev/
make

You will need around 200 MB (or more) for the dependencies.
